data.description: Nestled in Norwich!  Only 16 miles of Minot, just West of Surrey, and with an easy commute to MAFB! Leave the hustle and bustle behind and discover small town living.  With a little TLC, the possibilities are endless!  This home sits on a HUGE .65 acre lot and boasts an oversized detached 2 car garage, large shed, and wood privacy fencing.  There are two perfectly positioned mud porches, a spacious family room, large dining room, huge kitchen, large full bath, and the second bedroom, are all on the main level.  The Master Bedroom is spacious and is located on the upper level, offset with a large loft.  Laundry is located in the walk out, unfinished basement.  Tons of potential at a great price!  This home is being sold in AS IS CONDITION.  Call your favorite agent today!
